    <item>
      <title>雷·达利奥（Ray Dalio）说，关税动荡损害了美国因可靠性的声誉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/ray-dalio-says-tariff-turmoil-hurt-us-reputation-for-reliability</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Bridgewater Associates的亿万富翁创始人Ray Dalio表示，本周所有全球市场动荡之后，投资者遭受了“创伤，震惊或恐惧的元素”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/ray-dalio-says-tariff-turmoil-hurt-us-reputation-for-reliability</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 16:51:17 GMT</pubDate>
